    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait, a cold compress? i thought warmth helps blood flow and healing. if it's just a small thing, can't i just do the warm soak and put some Neosporin on it tonight and see how it looks in the morning? i feel like i'm overthinking it and i really just want a definitive way to handle this at home so i don't have to waste time at the doctor.",
